     <header>
        <h1>How to make a boiling water with milk</h1>
        <img src="https://i.imgur.com/Jj5kiDy.jpg"
        <p>There is nothing else so good than a cup o boiling water. There is my favourite recipe from all of them xD </p>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>500 ml of water (tap water is ok)
        </li>
        <li>1 hotpan 
        </li>
        <li> 20 ml of milk</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h3>Preparations</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>take a hotpan</li>
          <li>put water in a hotpan</li>
          <li>put hotpan with water on a stove and turn it on to 5</li>
          <li>wait 7 minutes till water boil</li>
          <li>if its boiled add 20 ml off milk</li>
          <li>water is ready, put it in your favorite cup and enjoy</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
